\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b0\fs24 New controls:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b\fs20 ColorSetter \b0 - in short a control made from 4 sliders and labels. Each slider represent RGBA color channels.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ColumnFilter \b0 - in short a control that allows user to specify a value used for "where" clause in SQL commands. This control shows different box based on filter type and generates different text based on filter mode.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b DataGridImageColumn \b0 - a DataGrid's template column used for showing an image.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ExtCheckBox \b0 - same as CheckBox but have different style for dark mode (poor version) and can display different icon depending on "IsError" property.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ExtComboBox \b0 - same as ComboBox but have different style for dark mode (poor version).\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ExtDataGrid \b0 - same as DataGrid but have different style for dark mode (poor version) and have additional properties for header brushes.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ExtImage \b0 - same as Image but have additional context menu that allows user to cut, copy, paste, delete, load and save an image.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ExtMenuItem \b0 - same as MenuItem but have image source property and creates Image as Icon at start.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ExtProgressBar \b0 - same as ProgressBar but have different style for dark mode (poor version) and can display text on progress bar.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ExtSeparator \b0 - same as Separator but have different style for dark mode (poor version) and can be displayed either horizontally or vertically.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ExtTextBox \b0 - same as TextBox. The only reason it exists is vertical content alignment centered by default.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ExtToggleButton \b0 - same as ToggleButton but have different style for dark mode (poor version) and is specially customized for MultiBox.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b Header \b0 - in short a control made from 2 images (one bigger and one smaller) and 2 text blocks.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b IconButton \b0 - in short a button made from image and text block.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b LoadingCircle \b0 - a control that displays rotating circle made from multiple Ellipses.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b MultiBox \b0 - in short a control that allows to select multiple items.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b NumericUpDown \b0 - in short a control made from text box and two repeat buttons allowing user to increase or decrese numeric value binded to box.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b OutlinedTextBlock \b0 - same as TextBlock but contains some properties allowing it to have a stroke.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b StswWindow \b0 - extended window with options to scale interface (poor version) and switch themes between light and dark.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs24 New helpers:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b\fs20 BindingProxy \b0 - helper class that allows creating a proxy object for data binding purposes.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b Commands \b0 - helper class that contains some routed UI commands including their input gestures.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b Converters \b0 - a collection of some converters such as: \b conv_Bool\b0 , \b conv_Color\b0 , \b conv_Compare\b0 , \b conv_Contains\b0 , \b conv_MultiCultureNumber\b0 , \b conv_NotNull\b0 , \b conv_Size\b0 , \b conv_StringToString\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b DB \b0 - helper class that is model for database connection and contains methods for import and export encrypted connection data to file.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b Extensions \b0 - a collection of some methods used like extensions such as: \b Between\b0 , \b Capitalize\b0 , \b ConvertTo\b0 , \b In\b0 , \b ToList\b0 , \b GetVisualChild\b0 , \b FindVisualChildren\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b Fn \b0 - a collection of some methods such as: \b AppName\b0 , \b AppVersion\b0 , \b AppNameAndVersion\b0 , \b AppCopyright\b0 , \b AppDatabase\b0 , \b AddCharBeforeUpperLetters\b0 , \b LoadImage\b0 , \b OpenContextMenu\b0 , \b OpenFile\b0 , \b GetWindowsThemeColor\b0 , \b GetColumnFilters\b0 , \b ClearColumnFilters\b0 , \b SetTheme\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b Log \b0 - helper class that allows to create log text entry in specified log file. After reaching a size limit, file is renamed and logs are saved to a new one.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b Mail \b0 - helpers class that is model for mailbox connection and contains method for sending mails.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b SQL \b0 - helper class to generate connection strings based on data from DB model class.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b Security \b0 - helper class that provides methods for encrypting and decrypting text and for generating salt and hash.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b VM \b0 - helper class implementing INotifyPropertyChanged interface that provides a method for invoking PropertyChanged.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs24 Other:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b\fs20 Resources \b0 - a collection of filter icons.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b Themes \b0 - a collection of styles for some controls to provide them with light and dark theme look (poor version).\par

