\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs24 New functionality:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs20 .NET version increased from 5 to 6.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}All controls and helping classes in library has been renamed and use "Stsw" prefix. Some of them have also completely changed names like \b ExtDatePicker \b0 -> \b StswCalendarPicker\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Many controls have been completely reworked, those with most changes are: \b StswColumnFilter\b0  (original name: ColumnFilter), \b StswHeader\b0  (original name: Header), \b LoadingCircle\b0 , \b StswProgressBar\b0  (original name: ExtProgressBar), \b StswWindow\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Completely new controls: \b ClippingBorder \b0 (to properly render content when CornerRadius is used), \b StswNavigation\b0 , \b StswNavigationButton\b0 , \b StswPasswordBox\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}New extension methods: \b AsBytes\b0 , \b ToNullable\b0 , \b ToStswDictionary\b0 , \b TrimEnd\b0  (with string as parameter), \b TrimStart\b0  (with string as parameter), \b TryMultipleTimes\b0  (that tries to execute an action or function multiple times with a specified interval between each try until it succeeds or reaches a maximum number of tries).\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}New classes: \b StswCollection \b0 (extended version of ObservableCollection - it notifies even if single item's property has changed and can contain info about states of items), \b StswDictionary\b0  (have INotifyProperty implemented and can be binded in a way that creates new key if it did not existed yet), \b StswExport\b0  (for exporting data to Excel file using "ClosedXML" library),\b  StswMC \b0 (meant to store mail configurations and sending mails), \b StswRelayCommand\b0  (have ICommand implemented and is meant to be binded to control command properties), \b StswSimpleModel \b0 (meant to be model for item sources in combo boxes).\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}New converters: \b conv_Add \b0 (that adds number from parameter to target number), \b conv_Calculate \b0 (that uses DataTable's compute method), \b conv_ColorBrightness\b0 , \b conv_IfElse\b0  (that displays one of two texts based on bool result of comparing), \b conv_NullToUnset\b0 , \b conv_Sum \b0 (that allows to sum field in list of class elements).\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Collection (7000+) of vector icons in new \b StswIcons \b0 static class.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b StswDataGrid \b0 has new special column for showing and clearing filters and showing row details.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b StswWindow \b0 has now fullscreen mode.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}TextBox based controls have placeholder functionality.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}New \b AppStart \b0 method meant to be put on application startup. This method sets all starting configuration needed for application to work properly if it is using Stsw controls and some of helpers.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}New project for library testing called \b TestApp\b0 . This version of test app has 3 simple modules: Database, Contractors, LibraryTests.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs24 Changed functionality:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs20 Themes are now based on external library called "DynamicAero2". There are two themes: \b Light \b0 and \b Dark\b0 , with possibility to auto select one of them based on system theme.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Many controls and functions have been adjusted to use them comfortably in MVVM.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Controls are now built on templates in styles in resource dictionaries.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Most of controls have "CornerRadius" property now.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b VM \b0 renamed into \b StswObservableObject\b0 . \b StswObservableObject \b0 have method called "SetProperty" that can be used in simple way in property setters.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b StswDB\b0  has been improved. Also the way \b StswDB \b0 and \b StswMC \b0 saves info into files is changed to keep every instance in one line.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b StswLog \b0 now works differently - before it was splitting every 5 MB into new file, now it groups logs per day of creation and makes a new file for each day.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b MultiBox\b0 's functionality\b  \b0 is merged into \b StswComboBox\b0  (when "SelectionMode" property is set to "Multiple").\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Converter \b conv_Contains \b0 no longer works only for IEnumerable. Converter \b conv_Compare \b0 has simplified functionality.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Controls like \b DataGridImage\b0 , \b ExtMenuItem\b0  and \b IconButton \b0 have been removed. Methods like \b AddCharBeforeUpperLetters\b0  have been removed.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Converter \b conv_Size\b0  has been renamed to \b conv_Multiply\b0 . Extension method named \b ToList \b0 has been renamed to \b AsList\b0 . Method extension \b GetVisualChild \b0 renamed to \b FindVisualChild\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Method \b ConvertTo \b0 made into extension method. Method \b LoadImage \b0 made into extension method named \b AsImage\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b BindingProxy\b0 's "Data" property renamed into "Proxy".\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b ColorSetter \b0 renamed to \b ColorPicker\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b StswNumericBox \b0 accepts changes after pressing Enter key.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b StswWindow \b0 now uses WindowChrome (that also eliminated some bugs and weird behavior).\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b StswSecurity \b0 class uses different algorithm for encrypting, decrypting and generating salt.\par

